{"id":163659,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/global-voices-克罗埃西亚：离加入欧盟又进一步/","date":"2011-06-25T07:30:18Z","modified":"2011-06-25T07:30:18Z","title":"Global Voices | 克罗埃西亚：离加入欧盟又进一步","content":"<p><p>2011年6月10日，<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-13725558\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-13725558\">克罗埃西亚</a>达到所有成为欧盟新成员国的条件，不过离正式入会还有很长一段路，且此刻欧盟也并不稳定，让许多人对未来存疑。</p>\n<p>除了欧洲目前经济局势动荡，在今年4月15日，南斯拉夫案国际法庭<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-13092438\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-13092438\">判决</a>前军事将领<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ante_Gotovina\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ante_Gotovina\">Ante Gotovina</a>和<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mladen_Marka%C4%8D\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mladen_Marka%C4%8D\">Mladen Markač</a>触犯战争罪。</p>\n<p><em>This Just In</em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/04/15/croatian-generals-convicted-of-war-crimes-crimes-against-humanity/\" href=\"http://news.blogs.cnn.com/2011/04/15/croatian-generals-convicted-of-war-crimes-crimes-against-humanity/\">指出</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>英国广播公司报导，听闻判决结果，克罗埃西亚首都中央广场的群众嘘声四起，在有些人心目中，这些将领是国家英雄。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/focaledesophieguesne/5638080159/in/photostream/\"><img title=\"Anti-EU protest on the day of ITCY convictions.\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/anti-eu-375x249.jpg\" alt=\"Anti-EU protest on the day of ITCY convictions. Image by Flickr user Sophie Guesné, used with permission.\" width=\"375\" height=\"249\" /></a></p>\n<p>南斯拉夫案国际法庭裁决出炉当天的反欧盟游行，照片来自Sophie Guesné</p>\n</div>\n<p>舆论对欧盟的看法很重要，因为在正式加入之前，克罗埃西亚必须先举办全国公投，若此刻投票，各项民调结果相距甚大，有些指称只有<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-12111568\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-12111568\">38%支持</a>，也有民调认为赞成者比例将<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.eubusiness.com/news-eu/croatia-enlarge.7fc/\" href=\"http://www.eubusiness.com/news-eu/croatia-enlarge.7fc/\">达64%</a>。</p>\n<p>尽管大众投票意向不明，克罗埃西亚政府仍继续鼓吹加入欧盟，<em>Jutarnji List</em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.jutarnji.hr/ulazak-hrvatske-u-eu--jadranka-kosor--ocekujem-potvrdu-europskog-vijeca-da-ce-hrvatska-do-kraja-lipnja-zavrsiti-pregovore-/954922/\" href=\"http://www.jutarnji.hr/ulazak-hrvatske-u-eu--jadranka-kosor--ocekujem-potvrdu-europskog-vijeca-da-ce-hrvatska-do-kraja-lipnja-zavrsiti-pregovore-/954922/\">提到</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jadranka_Kosor\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jadranka_Kosor\">总理</a>表示，克罗埃西亚值得为了进入欧盟而庆祝，尤其是我国在本周庆祝独立20周年，他强调，“我总认为这是独立周年纪念最佳礼物”。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>社会大众对此事不满之处，大多在于过程如此漫长，<em>gospon profesor</em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://gosponprofesor.blog.hr/2011/06/1629287132/daju-nam-ali-tako-da-im-ne-udemo.html\" href=\"http://gosponprofesor.blog.hr/2011/06/1629287132/daju-nam-ali-tako-da-im-ne-udemo.html\">写道</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>所以经过六项考验，现在还有两项？我原本以为谈判结束后，我们就进入欧盟了，但实际却不是这么回事。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>有人在<em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://kinkykolumnistica.blog.hr/\" href=\"http://kinkykolumnistica.blog.hr/\">Kinky Kolumnista</a></em>博客留言时，从务实角度看待入会程序：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>老实说，若无欧盟施压，国内不会出现这些小幅进步，我们也会继续深陷在泥泞之中，[…]欧盟国家显然比我们成功，未进入欧盟就会居于劣势。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>未来两年之内，克罗埃西亚还有众多尚待努力之处，但目前所有迹象看来，该国都将成为欧盟第28个会员。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/miquel-hudin/\" title=\"文章导读 Miquel Hudin\">Miquel Hudin</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/leonard/\" title=\"文章导读 Leonard\">Leonard</a> </span> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/06/23/croatia-eu-membership-approval/\" title=\"阅读原文 [en]\">阅读原文 [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/06/25/9416/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E5%85%8B%E7%BD%97%E5%9F%83%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E7%A6%BB%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%E5%8F%88%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F25%2F9416%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F25%2F9416%2F&#038;desc=%E5%85%8B%E7%BD%97%E5%9F%83%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E7%A6%BB%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%E5%8F%88%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F25%2F9416%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F25%2F9416%2F&#038;text=%E5%85%8B%E7%BD%97%E5%9F%83%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E7%A6%BB%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%E5%8F%88%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F25%2F9416%2F&#038;title=%E5%85%8B%E7%BD%97%E5%9F%83%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E7%A6%BB%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%E5%8F%88%E8%BF%9B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2